---
title: Cheesy Turkey Quesadillas with DIY Salsa and Lime Crema
description: These quick and easy quesadillas are loaded with turkey, peppers and lots of gooey melted cheese. Dunk the golden-brown wedges into cooling lime crema, bright salsa, or both! This meal is great to grab and go, any night of the week.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quesadillas-fromagees-a-la-dinde-c9cbc25a.jpg
